full_text: moon knight is cool and all but man is there some convenient writing going on with this thing

The play-in tournament is annoying and stupid. Literally 2/3 of the teams make the playoffs now, yet some great teams who earned a top 8 seed through 82 games can just have their season ended in a quick double elimination. Should just go back to 16 teams.
Guardians winning the World Series this year
